{"type":"message","id":"aa67ccd4","parentId":"e581d763","timestamp":"2026-04-14T00:00:00.892Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:da4546e3-8bdd-4291-b88f-472a4b5d4b34 盘前-MyQuant选股] 执行盘前 MyQuant 选股：\n1. 先检查今天是否交易日（2026年休市日：20260101 20260102 20260216-20260220 20260223 20260406 20260501 20260504 20260505 20260619 20260925 20261001-20261007），休市则输出\"休市\"结束\n2. 运行: cd /Users/lynch/Codes/MyQuant && /opt/miniconda3/envs/MyQuant/bin/python -m myquant preopen > /tmp/preopen_$(date +%Y%m%d).log 2>&1\n3. 等待完成（约2分钟，Tushare调用较多），检查 outputs/preopen/YYYYMMDD/ 下 top_y5.csv 是否存在且是新生成的（检查文件修改时间）\n4. 如果成功，输出\"preopen 完成，候选池 N 只\"；如果失败，输出错误信息\nCurrent time: Tuesday, April 14th, 2026 — 08:00 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-14 00:00 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1776124800889}}
{"type":"message","id":"67a8b908","parentId":"aa67ccd4","timestamp":"2026-04-14T00:00:46.849Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\nLet me analyze this cron job request. The user is asking me to execute a pre-market stock selection task using MyQuant. The task has the following steps:\n\n1. Check if today (2026-04-14) is a trading day\n2. If it's a trading day, run a MyQuant pre-open selection command\n3. Check if the output file was generated\n4. Report success or failure\n\nFirst, I need to check if today is a trading day. Looking at the provided list of holidays for 2026:\n- 20260101, 20260102\n- 20260216-20260220 (week of Chinese New Year)\n- 20260223\n- 20260406\n- 20260501, 20260504, 20260505\n- 20260619\n- 20260925\n- 20261001-20261007 (National Day holiday)\n\nToday is 2026-04-14, which is not in the holiday list, so it should be a trading day.\n\nNext, I need to run the MyQuant command:\n```bash\ncd /Users/lynch/Codes/MyQuant && /opt/miniconda3/envs/MyQuant/bin/python -m myquant preopen > /tmp/preopen_$(date +%Y%m%d).log 2>&1\n```\n\nThen I need to check if the output file exists at `outputs/preopen/YYYYMMDD/top_y5.csv` where YYYYMMDD would be 20260414.\n\nLet me execute this step by step.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n<thinking>\nLet me break down this cron task:\n\n1. First, I need to check if 2026-04-14 is a trading day by checking if it's in the holiday list\n2. If it is a trading day, run the MyQuant pre-open command\n3. Check if the output file was generated\n4. Report the result\n\nLooking at the holiday list:\n- 20260101, 20260102\n- 20260216-20260220 \n- 20260223\n- 20260406\n- 20260501, 20260504, 20260505\n- 20260619\n- 20260925\n- 20261001-20261007\n\nToday is 2026-04-14, which is NOT in the holiday list, so it should be a trading day.\n\nLet me execute the task step by step.\n</thinking>\n\nI'll execute the pre-market MyQuant stock selection task. Let me start by checking if today is a trading day and then run the process.\n\n## Step 1: Check if today is a trading day\nToday is 2026-04-14. Checking against the holiday list:\n- Holidays: 20260101, 20260102, 20260216-20260220, 20260223, 20260406, 20260501, 20260504, 20260505, 20260619, 20260925, 20261001-20261007\n- 2026-04-14 is NOT in the holiday list ✓\n\n**Result: Today is a trading day**\n\n## Step 2: Run MyQuant pre-open selection\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_dda75960d11d4ce2a60662c1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/lynch/Codes/MyQuant && /opt/miniconda3/envs/MyQuant/bin/python -m myquant preopen > /tmp/preopen_20260414.log 2>&1","timeout":180000}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-customb2","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":37203,"output":786,"cacheRead":5268,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43257,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776124800891,"responseId":"20260414080001e0130f4d87af4a07"}}
